 Explain how to find the derivative \(f'(x)\). 

 \[
f(x)=-3 \, e^{x} \log\left(x\right)
        \] \end{exerciseStatement}
 \begin{exerciseAnswer} \[
f'(x)=-3 \, e^{x} \log\left(x\right) - \frac{3 \, e^{x}}{x}
        \] \end{exerciseAnswer}
 \end{exercise}

